### SwaRupa API — Comprehensive Endpoint Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### Note: UUIDs in URLs should be replaced with actual IDs from API responses
@access_token = REPLACE_WITH_SUPABASE_ACCESS_TOKEN


# ==============================================================
# HEALTH & WELCOME
# ==============================================================

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

---

### Welcome
GET http://localhost:8080/api/welcome


# ==============================================================
# USERS
# ==============================================================

### 1. Create User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "user_001",
  "display_name": "Alice Admin"
}

---

### 2. Create User — missing id (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "display_name": "No ID User"
}

---

### 3. Get User by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/user_001

---

### 4. Get User — not found (expect 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/nonexistent_user

---

### 5. Get All Users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users

---

### 6. Get All Users — with pagination (page 1, 20 per page)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users?page=1&limit=20

---

### 6a. Link Provider Account (authenticated)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/link-provider
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "provider_user_id": "legacy_email_user_id"
}


# ==============================================================
# ARTISTS
# ==============================================================

### 7. Create Artist — full fields
POST http://localhost:8080/api/artists
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "name": "Sushmit Fernando",
  "artist_bio": "Sri Lankan music producer",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/sushmit.jpg"
}

---

### 8. Create Artist — minimal (name only)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/artists
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "name": "Thom Yorke"
}

---

### 9. Create Artist — missing name (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/artists
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "image_url": "https://example.com/image.jpg"
}

---

### 10. Get Artist by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/artists/ARTIST_ID_1

---

### 11. Get Artist — not found (expect 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/artists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

---

### 12. Get All Artists (paginated)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/artists

---

### 13. Get All Artists — page 1, limit 10
GET http://localhost:8080/api/artists?page=1&limit=10

---

### 14. Get All Artists — page 2, limit 20
GET http://localhost:8080/api/artists?page=2&limit=20

---

### 15. Get All Artists — limit max (100)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/artists?limit=100

---

### Search Artists — exact name match
GET http://localhost:8080/search/artists?q=Sushmit

---

### Search Artists — partial name match
GET http://localhost:8080/search/artists?q=Shum

---

### Search Artists — with pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/search/artists?q=Radiohead&page=1&limit=20

---

### Search Artists — missing query (expect 400)
GET http://localhost:8080/search/artists


# ==============================================================
# ALBUMS
# ==============================================================

### 16. Create Album — single artist
POST http://localhost:8080/api/albums
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "title": "Silent Lanterns",
  "release_year": 2023,
  "artist_ids": ["ARTIST_ID_1"]
}

---

### 17. Create Album — multiple artists
POST http://localhost:8080/api/albums
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "title": "Collaborative Work",
  "release_year": 2024,
  "artist_ids": ["ARTIST_ID_1", "ARTIST_ID_2"]
}

---

### 18. Create Album — no release year (optional)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/albums
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "title": "Untitled Album",
  "artist_ids": ["ARTIST_ID_1"]
}

---

### 19. Create Album — missing title (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/albums
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "release_year": 2024,
  "artist_ids": ["ARTIST_ID_1"]
}

---

### 20. Create Album — missing artist_ids (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/albums
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "title": "No Artists Album"
}

---

### 21. Create Album — empty artist_ids (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/albums
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "title": "Empty Artists",
  "artist_ids": []
}

---

