# ==============================================================
# ARTWORKS (Submission & Retrieval)
# ==============================================================

### 27. Submit Artwork — with source details
POST http://localhost:8080/api/albums/ALBUM_ID_1/artworks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "source_name": "official",
  "source_page": "https://example.com/album",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/cover.jpg",
  "source_type": "official",
  "confidence_score": 1.0,
  "quality_score": 0.95
}

---

### 28. Submit Artwork — minimal
POST http://localhost:8080/api/albums/ALBUM_ID_1/artworks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "source_name": "user_upload",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/fan-art.jpg"
}

---

### 29. Submit Artwork — missing image_url (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/albums/ALBUM_ID_1/artworks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "source_name": "gallery"
}

---

### 30. Get Artworks for Album — no filters
GET http://localhost:8080/api/albums/ALBUM_ID_1/artworks

---

### 31. Get Artworks for Album — paginated (page 1, limit 10)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/albums/ALBUM_ID_1/artworks?page=1&limit=10

---

### 32. Get Artworks for Album — filter by pending status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/albums/ALBUM_ID_1/artworks?status=pending

---

### 33. Get Artworks for Album — filter by approved status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/albums/ALBUM_ID_1/artworks?status=approved

---

### 34. Get Artworks for Album — filter by rejected status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/albums/ALBUM_ID_1/artworks?status=rejected

---

### 35. Get Artworks for Album — official only
GET http://localhost:8080/api/albums/ALBUM_ID_1/artworks?official=true

---

### 36. Get Artworks for Album — sort by priority score
GET http://localhost:8080/api/albums/ALBUM_ID_1/artworks?sort=priority

---

### 37. Get Artworks for Album — combined: approved + priority
GET http://localhost:8080/api/albums/ALBUM_ID_1/artworks?status=approved&sort=priority&page=1&limit=20

---

### 38. Get All Artworks across albums
GET http://localhost:8080/api/artworks

---

### 39. Get All Artworks — filter by approved
GET http://localhost:8080/api/artworks?status=approved

---

### 40. Get All Artworks — official only
GET http://localhost:8080/api/artworks?official=true&sort=priority


# ==============================================================
# ARTWORK SOURCES (Phase 3)
# ==============================================================

### 41. Add Source to Artwork
POST http://localhost:8080/api/artworks/ARTWORK_ID_1/sources
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "source_name": "spotify",
  "source_page": "https://open.spotify.com/album/xyz",
  "image_url": "https://image.spotify.com/cover.jpg"
}

---

### 42. Add Source — missing source_name (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/artworks/ARTWORK_ID_1/sources
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "source_page": "https://example.com",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/image.jpg"
}

---

### 43. List All Sources for Artwork
GET http://localhost:8080/api/artworks/ARTWORK_ID_1/sources

---

### 44. List Sources — artwork without sources (expect empty array)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/artworks/ARTWORK_ID_2/sources

---

### 45. Update Artwork Source Scores
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/artworks/ARTWORK_ID_1/sources/SOURCE_ID_1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confidence_score": 0.95,
  "quality_score": 0.88
}

---

### 46. Update Source — missing confidence_score (expect 400)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/artworks/ARTWORK_ID_1/sources/SOURCE_ID_1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quality_score": 0.88
}

---

### 47. Delete Artwork Source
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/artworks/ARTWORK_ID_1/sources/SOURCE_ID_1

---

### 48. Delete Source — not found (expect error)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/artworks/ARTWORK_ID_1/sources/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000


